to grab a bite to eat sometime.

52:34.160 --> 52:36.800
Well, I could eat now.

52:38.040 --> 52:39.560
Then shall we?

52:42.800 --> 52:45.640
So how long have you been divorced?
About 18 months.

52:45.640 --> 52:47.000
